Here’s a **short standalone CSS** snippet for **Dino Dash** (put it in a `style.css` and link it in the HTML):

```css
/* Dino Dash Styles */
body {
  margin: 0;
  background: #e0f7fa;
  font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif;
  text-align: center;
}

h2 {
  margin: 10px;
  color: #333;
}

canvas {
  background: #fff;
  display: block;
  margin: 20px auto;
  border: 2px solid #333;
  border-radius: 8px;
}

button {
  padding: 8px 14px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 6px;
  background: #ff7043;
  color: #fff;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-weight: bold;
  transition: background 0.3s;
}

button:hover {
  background: #f4511e;
}
```

